>Редактор дроблень із непризначеною сумою</phrase>
    </textobject>
  </mediaobject>
</screenshot>

<para
>To enter a new split or sub-transaction click <guibutton
>New</guibutton
>, press <keycombo action="simul"
>&Ctrl;&Ins;</keycombo
>, or double-click an empty row. Double-clicking an existing row lets you edit the split. This will expand the row into form where you can enter or edit a split. </para
> 

